<p id="u3278-6"><span id="u3278">Metropolitan has created easy-to-follow booklets and reference materials to help homeowners, businesses and institutions like hospitals, schools and universities identify ways to save water. Here you’ll find downloadable waterwise tip cards, California Friendly® gardening </span><span class="Body-text" id="u3278-2">guides, how</span><span id="u3278-3">-to video</span><span class="Body-text" id="u3278-4">s and o</span><span id="u3278-5">riginal artwork from our latest advertising and outreach campaign.</span></p>
